title: The Adventures of Mr. Pickle

creator: Steven Tu
descriptionHtml:
The Kingdom of Pickle Land exists as the central nation of a domain of interconnected island civilizations resting on a large oasis of an unknown desert.

Mr. Pickle, an avid adventurer who seeks to bring glory to his kingdom, begins to encounter an increasing number of strange occurrences within the land, to which he begins to learn are part of something much more malicious.

Mr. Pickle, an avid adventurer who seeks to bring glory to his kingdom, begins to encounter an increasing number of strange occurrences within the land, to which he begins to learn are part of something much more malicious.
